          <a data-translate="hakkimizda.breadcrumb.aboutUs" href="aboutus">
            About Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content-body">
        <h1 class="page-title-2" data-translate="hakkimizda.content.pageTitle">
          About BFM
        </h1>
        <div class="content-text">
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.missionTitle">
            Our Mission:
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-5" data-translate="hakkimizda.content.missionText">
            To directly contribute to our country's
            exports by supporting our companies' access to new markets both nationally and internationally.
          </p>
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.visionTitle">
            Our Vision:
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-5" data-translate="hakkimizda.content.visionText">
            To be Turkey's leading exhibition center,
            offering services at international standards, with a constantly renewed, high-level infrastructure, and an
            approach that exceeds exhibitor and visitor satisfaction.
          </p>
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.valuesTitle">
            Our values:
          </h3>
          <ul>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.values.0">
              Customer Focus
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.values.1">
              Clearness
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.values.2">
              Reliability
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.values.3">
              Innovation
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.values.4">
              Teamwork
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.values.5">
              Sustainability
            </li>
          </ul>
          <br />
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.historyTitle">
            Our Establishment and Development Process
          </h3>
          <p data-translate="hakkimizda.content.historyText1">
            Bursa Fair Center (BFM) was taken over by BTSO
            subsidiary KFA Fair Organization Inc. in 2025 and completed extensive renovations. This transformation,
            led by BTSO's over 30 years of experience, has modernized our fair physically and organizationally.
          </p>
          <p data-translate="hakkimizda.content.historyText2">
            Following its renovation, BFM hosted the first-ever
            Rising City &amp; Building and Living Fair from April 24–27, 2025.

            Bringing together approximately 40 companies with over 200 foreign buyers from 16 countries, it
            strengthened its regional and international presence.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-5" data-translate="hakkimizda.content.historyText3">
            Together with KFA Fair Organization, we aim
            to make Bursa a brand city in the field of fair organization, with the goal of organizing over 20
            international fairs every year at BFM.
          </p>
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsTitle">
            Our Infrastructure and Capacity
          </h3>
          <ul class="mb-5">
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsArea">
              Total Area: 140,000 m² (Closed: ~40,000 m² / Open:
              ~100,000 m²)
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsIndoorArea">
              Number of Halls: 6
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsOutdoorArea">
              Meeting Rooms: 15
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsHalls">
              Annual Fair Hosting: 20+ international events targeted
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsTitle">
            Location and Transportation
          </h3>
          <ul class="mb-5">
            <p class="fs-5">
              BFM is easily accessible thanks to its location close to the city center;
            </p>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsArea">
              Just a few kilometers from Bursa city center,
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsIndoorArea">
              Approximately 45 km from Yenişehir Airport,
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsOutdoorArea">
              Istanbul Sabiha Gökçen Airport is approximately
              1.5 hours away.
              Access is seamless via public transportation and commercial vehicles.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsTitle">
            Our Service Scope
          </h3>
          <ul class="mb-5">
            <p class="fs-5">
              We provide exhibitors and visitors with:
            </p>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsArea">
              Fair organization
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsIndoorArea">
              Professional stand design and installation
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsOutdoorArea">
              Technical support services
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsIndoorArea">
              Accommodation and transportation arrangements
            </li>
            <li data-translate="hakkimizda.content.statsIndoorArea">
              Food and beverage experiences and other logistical
              support
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h3 data-translate="hakkimizda.content.collaborationTitle">
            Collaborations and Added Value Our Approach
          </h3>
          <p class="mb-5" data-translate="hakkimizda.content.collaborationText">
            We place great importance on
            collaboration with local and national stakeholders, particularly BTSO. Through this synergy, we aim to
            increase participant satisfaction, contribute to their business development, and contribute to Bursa's
            export potential.
          </p>
